            <title>[SWTES0707-125] [TG-5] [Teodora] Poll creation - wrong time in the review poll screen</title>
                <link>http://jira.softacad.bg/browse/SWTES0707-125</link>
                <project id="11900" key="SWTES0707">SW_Test_07_07_2020	</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After creating a poll, the user is redirected to the review poll screen - the time left for the poll is wrong.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Steps to reproduce:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1.Navigate to&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;http://poll-app7-20200409.softacad.bg/poll/new&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://poll-app7-20200409.softacad.bg/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2.Login with valid credentials and click the New Poll icon.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3. Write a question with 2 choices:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Do you like pineapple on pizza?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Yes&#160;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;No&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;4. Make the poll length 1 day.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;5.Click Create Poll button.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Expected result:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The user is redirected to&#160;the review poll screen where he can see the question with the information exactly as he wrote it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Actual result:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The information is not correct. For poll length instead of 24 hours, it says 23 hours.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
